### EduPortal API - Payment Installments Controller
### Payment installment management endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/payment-installments
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### GET INSTALLMENT BY ID
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET INSTALLMENTS BY PLAN
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/plan/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET INSTALLMENTS BY STUDENT
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET OVERDUE INSTALLMENTS - (Admin, Muhasebe)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/overdue
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET UPCOMING INSTALLMENTS - (Admin, Muhasebe)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/upcoming?days=7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### PAY INSTALLMENT - (Admin, Muhasebe)
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/1/pay
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "paidAmount": 5000.00,
  "paymentMethod": "CreditCard",
  "transactionId": "TXN123456789",
  "notes": "Ödeme başarılı"
}

### ===========================================
### GET STATISTICS - (Admin, Muhasebe)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
